                                                                 BUSISNESS QUESTION
Which customers respond best to discounts, and are they profitable?

           QUERY
SELECT
CASE
WHEN lifetime_value > 2000 then 'high value customers'
WHEN lifetime_value > 1000 then 'mid value customers'
ELSE 'low value customers'
END AS Customers_status,
ROUND(AVG(discount_usage_rate),2) avg_discount,
ROUND(AVG(lifetime_value) ,2)total_revenue
FROM ecommerce_data
GROUP BY Customers_status;

                     Insight
Mid-value customers respond more to discounts compared to other groups, showing they are more sensitive to pricing.

                Recommendation 
Discounts should be used carefully and not too frequently. Other incentives can also be introduced to avoid reducing profit.
